modules.description: Processes TextMate grammar files and applies them to tokenize source code lines, enabling precise syntax analysis. Operates on structured grammar definitions and raw string input to produce token streams. Used to build custom syntax highlighters with accurate token classification.

Creates and manages a collection of TextMate grammars, enabling lookup by name, scope, or file type. Parses grammars from PLIST and JSON formats, and tokenizes lines of code using defined grammars. Tracks tokenization state to process code line by line with accurate scope and position information.
